com.geotask.myapplication.Controllers

Class MasterController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.geotask.myapplication.Controllers.MasterController

  • public class MasterController
extends java.lang.Object
    All data management goes through here. This controller will keep local SQL database synced to the server. Contains ElasticsearchController and 3 DatabaseController. Do not call ElasticSearchController and DatabaseControllers explicitly, use this instead.
